        <item>
            <title>1.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 08:28:12 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.2.0</h2>
<p>Otto can now text you and call your phone, using your own Twilio account. Set it up in Settings under Text & calls, then pick how your morning briefing arrives — spoken, texted, or as a phone call. Otto only ever reaches your own number.</p>
]]></description>
